name: DogBark
overview:
DogBark.com is a reliable and Mac friendly web hosting company run by fun, friendly, loyal & experienced staff. DogBark here to help you out in any way possible - on the phone (866-DOG-BARK), via email or via chat. Need help setting up your iPhone? No problem - DogBark’s North American staff will patiently walk you through it on the phone. FTP program not connecting? Our team can remotely connect to your computer and fix it for you!

DogBark.com also offers a one-click installer that lets you install Blogs, Forums and other interactive software on your website. Don’t know how to use it? DogBark will walk you through it :)

DogBark is your best friend for web hosting solutions.
